OL,3,CGoing the Extra Mile: The harsh
OL,4,Crealities of a night on the town for
OL,5,Csome
OL,7,FThe figures for homeless deaths have
OL,8,Fbeen published in Northern Ireland for
OL,9,Fthe first time and while they
OL,10,Frightfully have prompted calls for
OL,11,Faction, for those working on the
OL,12,Ffrontline, the fact that over fifty
OL,13,Fpeople are dying on our streets every
OL,14,Fyear comes as no surprise and that
OL,15,Fthings are getting worse.
OL,17,FDamian McNairney is a volunteer and
OL,18,Ftrustee at the People's Kitchen in
OL,19,FBelfast.
