OL,3,CGoing the Extra Mile: The harsh
OL,4,Crealities of a night on the town for
OL,5,Csome
OL,7,FA social worker by day, Damian spends
OL,8,Fmuch of his spare time volunteering
OL,9,Fwith rough sleepers and people with
OL,10,Fsubstance abuse issues, two issues
OL,11,Fwhich are tragically intertwined.
OL,13,FFor him, the figures which have been
OL,14,Freleased by the Northern Ireland
OL,15,FStatistics and Research Agency, only
OL,16,Fpaint part of a very complicated
OL,17,Fpicture.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
