OL,3,CGoing the Extra Mile: The harsh
OL,4,Crealities of a night on the town for
OL,5,Csome
OL,7,F"Sadly I'm not surprised at all. This
OL,8,Fhas been a trend ... These figures are
OL,9,Fjust evidence of what we've been
OL,10,Fsaying all along and those figures
OL,11,Fwill increase. We're only in the
OL,12,Ffoothills of the winter now and the
OL,13,Fnumber of people who will die in the
OL,14,Fstreets will definitely increase," he
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FDamian has faced his own challenges
OL,18,Fwith mental health and it is this
OL,19,Fwhich he says have inspired him to
OL,20,Fhelp others.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
