OL,3,CGoing the Extra Mile: The harsh
OL,4,Crealities of a night on the town for
OL,5,Csome
OL,7,F"I hope it's given me a layer of
OL,8,Fempathy to encourage people to open
OL,9,Fup, to let them know that there are
OL,10,Fpeople there that they can speak to. I
OL,11,Fthink sometimes the best question you
OL,12,Fcan ask is to listen. And I think
OL,13,Fthat's what I learned through my
OL,14,Fjourney," he told the Going the Extra
OL,15,FMile Podcast.
OL,17,FFor Damian, the outreach work is
OL,18,Fparamount but he says to seriously
OL,19,Ftackle the issue of homelessness takes
OL,20,Fa multi-agency approach.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
