OL,3,CGoing the Extra Mile: The harsh
OL,4,Crealities of a night on the town for
OL,5,Csome
OL,7,FThe People's Kitchen is calling for a
OL,8,Fcharter which outlines how to combat
OL,9,Fthe problem.JI ask Damian if he thinks
OL,10,Fthat there is a public desensitisation
OL,11,Fto the issue of rough sleepers too?
OL,13,FMany of us at this time of the year
OL,14,Fare Christmas shopping, walking past
OL,15,Fthose seeking shelter in shop fronts,
OL,16,Findulging in the excess but does this
OL,17,Fexacerbate the sense that our society
OL,18,Fhas become fractured into the haves
OL,19,Fand the have nothings?
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
