OL,7,FUTV put the points made by Damian to
OL,8,Fthe Department of Communities and they
OL,9,Fhave referred us to recent press
OL,10,Freleases where the Minister has
OL,11,Fannounced additional funding for
OL,12,Fhomeless services, and the launch of
OL,13,FNew Foundations, an cross-departmental
OL,14,Finitiative to house young care leavers
OL,15,Fand help prevent homelessness.
